cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper discusses the use of artificial neoteny in a genetic algorithm for image segmentation, which falls under the categories of neural networks and machine learning (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves clustering and classification, which could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and graphics (cs.GR).
